data.message:
Hey Em, check out my rap! Its a diss to a friend:
While Dilan the Villain,
was sniffing vanilla on his whores back in Milan,
there was ppl outside, wanting to kill 'em.
"Noone's killing us Jane, we're safe, dont worry" he said,
"Imma take my gun at last, and burry them fast"
Dilan the Villain, then took his machine gun,
rushed to the window and thus the fight begun.
Bullets were flying, by Dilans ears and then by Dilan's dick
Last bullet made him understand, its not worth it, not a single shit
He then turned around, and grabbed his chick
Threw her over the window and said "Take this bitch!"
Shooting stopped, cars turned around
Dillan cried, cried so much
He then got up, and went downtown
While he was walking, he was still mocking
Cars ran by, dilan cried
And then 1 moment, he decided
Jumped in front of a car, misguided.
Thus the story of Dilan the Villain ended,
Hope noone got offended.
